{"TopicId":194549,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Destroy the KSC Challenge","CreatedByName":"Jebediah Kerman Jr.","CreatedById":189524,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-08T02:12:56Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jebediah Kerman Jr.","CreatedById":189524,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-08T02:12:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs above. The rules are simple: you must destroy as many of the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E buildings\u00A0as possible with a single \u003Cstrong\u003Estock\u003C/strong\u003E vehicle. It can be a rocket, a plane, a rover,\u00A0etc. Your vessel can drop bombs, break into pieces, or whatever it takes to cause as much chaos as possible in the shortest possible time. I\u0027ll make badges for the winners of the challenge.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere are the different levels:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClass \u003Cstrong\u003E1\u003C/strong\u003E: Destroy three Space Center buildings with a single vessel.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClass \u003Cstrong\u003E2\u003C/strong\u003E:\u00A0Destroy five Space Center buildings with a single vessel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClass \u003Cstrong\u003E2.5\u003C/strong\u003E: Destroy seven or more Space Center buildings with a single vessel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClass \u003Cstrong\u003E3\u003C/strong\u003E: Destroy every Space Center building with a single vessel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClass \u003Cb style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#202122;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16.52px;\u0022\u003E\u03C0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/b\u003E: Destroy every single building, water tower, flagpole, gas tank, command pod memorial, etc. with a single vessel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClass \u003Cstrong\u003E???\u003C/strong\u003E: Destroy at least three buildings using a projectile dropped from orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood luck!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ralanboyle","CreatedById":201693,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-08T13:11:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/fi1smNXs35g?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jebediah Kerman Jr.","CreatedById":189524,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-08T14:27:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223799252\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194549\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591621887\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022201693\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ralanboyle\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, ralanboyle said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/fi1smNXs35g?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hereby award you\u00A0\u003Ci\u003ECLASS 2.5\u003C/i\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"doggonemess","CreatedById":160106,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-08T14:46:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFUN!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/DCocigYXoPk?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-08T21:46:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe might want to make separate categories for 1.8 and above, as the math changed and the Space Center went from ridiculously fragile to ridiculously durable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-08T21:51:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust sn FYI for ideas:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022149302\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1639646120\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/167335-ksp-challenge-destroy-the-ksc/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:213px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jebediah Kerman Jr.","CreatedById":189524,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-09T13:03:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223799545\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194549\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591653108\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 hours ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust sn FYI for ideas:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022149302\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1548628067\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/167335-ksp-challenge-destroy-the-ksc/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, it\u0027s already been done.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sevenperforce","CreatedById":157695,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-09T16:34:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223799543\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194549\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591652773\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pds314\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, Pds314 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe might want to make separate categories for 1.8 and above, as the math changed and the Space Center went from ridiculously fragile to ridiculously durable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah I have been dropping ore tanks on it with increasing weight and it\u0027s shocking how durable it is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ralanboyle","CreatedById":201693,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-09T19:35:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223799983\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194549\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591720465\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157695\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sevenperforce\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, sevenperforce said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah I have been dropping ore tanks on it with increasing weight and it\u0027s shocking how durable it is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is why I ended up shooting full kickbacks at them... it\u2019s silly how much it takes even if you turn the setting down.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-09T20:41:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was thinking about building an orbital platform...but I play on console, so there\u0027s no way I could legitimately do this challenge, even with the damage settings kicked up all the way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sevenperforce","CreatedById":157695,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-11T20:07:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith damage kicked up all the way, two large ore tanks hitting the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E above 289 m/s will destroy it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTrying to see if lower mass and higher velocity will do it too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT:\u00A0A single large ore tank will destroy the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E at 417 m/s but not at 414 m/s so that\u0027s probably about our cutoff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTerminal velocity of a large unshielded ore tank is about 310 m/s.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT II: A single large ore tank with fairings on the nose and tail impacts at well in excess of 900 m/s when dropped from orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-06-11T20:32:06Z\u0022 title=\u002206/11/2020 08:32  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJune 11, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by sevenperforce\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}